name: Palmer Penguins
content:
Description: Data on penguins at Palmer Station LTER, located in Antarctica.

[Source](https://github.com/rfordatascience/tidytuesday/blob/master/data/2020/2020-07-28/readme.md) and second [source](https://allisonhorst.github.io/palmerpenguins/)

Columns:

 * species (string): Penguin species (Adelie, Gentoo, Chinstrap)
 * island (string): Island where recorded (Biscoe, Dream, Torgersen)
 * bill_length_mm (numerical): Bill length in millimeters (also known as culmen length) in millimeters
 * bill_depth_mm (numerical): Bill depth in millimeters (also known as culmen depth) in millimeters
 * flipper_length_mm (numerical): Flipper length in mm
 * body_mass_g (numerical): Body mass in grams
 * sex (string): sex of the animal
 * year (string): year recorded
